        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml\nskinparam node {\n    BackgroundColor LightCyan\n    BorderColor DarkCyan\n}\nskinparam component {\n    BackgroundColor White\n    BorderColor #333333\n}\nskinparam arrowColor DimGray\n\ntitle Observability &amp; Telemetry Architecture (Наблюдаемост)\n\nnode \&quot;EcoProject Application Layer\&quot; {\n    component \&quot;React Frontend\&quot; as UI\n    component \&quot;.NET 8 API (AI Assistant)\&quot; as API\n}\n\nnode \&quot;Telemetry &amp; Logging Stack\&quot; {\n    component \&quot;Structured Logging\\n(Serilog / NLog)\&quot; as Logger\n    component \&quot;Metrics Collector\\n(OpenTelemetry)\&quot; as Metrics\n}\n\nnode \&quot;Monitoring &amp; Alerting Dashboards\&quot; {\n    database \&quot;Log Storage\\n(Elasticsearch / Seq)\&quot; as LogDB\n    component \&quot;Grafana Dashboard\\n(Визуализация)\&quot; as Grafana\n    component \&quot;Alerting System\\n(Имейл/Slack при срив на AI)\&quot; as Alerts\n}\n\nUI --&gt; Logger : \&quot;Грешки в конзолата (JS Errors)\&quot;\nAPI --&gt; Logger : \&quot;Инфо, Грешки, Fallback събития\&quot;\nAPI --&gt; Metrics : \&quot;AI Latency, Shadow Mode Telemetry\&quot;\n\nLogger --&gt; LogDB : \&quot;Запазване на логове\&quot;\nMetrics --&gt; Grafana : \&quot;Подаване на метрики\&quot;\nLogDB --&gt; Grafana : \&quot;Търсене в логовете\&quot;\n\nGrafana --&gt; Alerts : \&quot;Ако Fallback Rate &gt; 20%\&quot;\n\nnote right of API\n  Записва специална телеметрия, \n  когато Shadow Mode е активен,\n  за да сравнява Gemini и OpenAI.\nend note\n\n@enduml&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="C2r3sth5Y2Ggru8Y6FEm-1">
